        <num>CC 308</num>
        <heading>308.  Duty to apply for appointment</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 308.  Duty to apply for appointment.
In every case where it is necessary to appoint a tutor to a minor, all those of his relations who reside within the parish of the judge, who is to appoint him, are bound to apply to such judge, in order that a tutor be appointed to the minor at farthest within ten days after the event which make [makes] such appointment necessary.</p>
        </content>
